quran[11]{c,v,t,f}:
  96,13,"Bal ka warran hadduu kaasina (gaalka ahi) beeniyo Xaqa, kana jeesado?"
  96,14,"Mawuusan ogeyn in Alle arko?"
  96,15,"Mayee! Haddii uusan meel joogin, waxaanu hubaal qaban foodda,"
  98,7,"Kuwa (Xaqa) rumeeyey oo samaha fala, kuwaasi waa kuwa ugu khayr badan uumanka."
  98,8,"Abaalkooda Rabbigood agtiis ah waa Beero negaadi ah (Jannooyin) oo ay hoostoodu webiyadu qul-qulaan, ay ku waari weligood, Alle Raalli buu ka yahay, iyaguna Raalli ku yihiin. Sidaas waxaa leh qofkii ka baqa Rabbigi oo ka dhowrsada xumaha."
  99,4,"Maalintaas waxay ka warrami akhbaarteeda."
  99,5,"Inuu Rabbigaa u waxyooday darteed."
  99,6,"Maalintaas dadku wuxuu u soo dareeri rac rac si loo tusiyo (jazaha)acmaashooda."
  100,1,"Waxaan (waa Alle'e) ku dhaartay ordayaasha dheereeya iyagoo qaylyi (fardaha dagaalka, iwm)."
  100,2,"Iyo kuwa kiciya dhimbilaha dabka."
  100,3,"Iyo kuwa (cadowga) weerara subaxa horeba,"
